992
01:27:40,289 --> 01:27:42,375
Aku tak mau uangmu. ⁄ Ya.

993
01:27:44,502 --> 01:27:45,753
Itu.

994
01:27:46,838 --> 01:27:48,047
Tuan-tuan...

995
01:27:49,257 --> 01:27:51,551
...bisakah kita tak tampak
